{"tid":1273864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雙普選宣言，認同請轉發","createTime":"2019-07-01T15:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T00:58:42.000Z","uid":266060,"like":88,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1c58de48f9abe49a17a83469ed07130cc5b02e1f","tid":1273864,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:03:35.000Z","msg":"<strong>《香港人的宣言：事到如今》</strong><br />\n<br />\n在回歸22年之際，香港發生一場觸目驚心的六月風暴，戳破了這22年來的幻象。<br />\n<br />\n我們看見，立法會並不對香港社會負責，即使反送中的民意清晰，百萬人上街，建制派憑功能組別的優勢，仍然計劃二讀通過。<br />\n<br />\n我們看見，特首並不對香港人負責，即使二百萬人上街，要求林鄭月娥下台，她仍然聲稱要繼續服務市民，完全違反民主精神。<br />\n<br />\n我們看見，特區政府在立法會的加持、人大常委會的釋法威脅下，主宰了香港的法律制度，DQ民選議員、通過一地兩檢，甚至打算以政治壓力強行引渡疑犯往內地，赤裸裸地侮辱香港法院。<br />\n<br />\n我們看見，特區政府在過去多年以來，政策向既得利益者傾斜，令貧者無立錐之地，香港淪為炒地、炒樓、炒奶粉的城市，年輕人看不見將來。<br />\n<br />\n政治問責、司法獨立、繁榮安定，全部都是不實的幻影，只是官方在愚弄大眾、合理化其專制統治之托詞。此荒唐的現實，在香港回歸22年之際，香港人及國際社會均看得清楚明白，連年輕的新一代都明知後果地上街拼命抗爭，戳破國王新衣的赤裸真相。<br />\n<br />\n沒有人想香港沉淪，但香港已經再走不下去，特區政府亦再沒有任何認受性，這是沒有人能否認的現實。事到如今，已經別無他法且等無可等，特區政府必須立即重啟政改，落實《基本法》第45條及第68條的莊嚴承諾，即特首及全體立法會由普選產生。唯有這樣才能挽救香港，亦唯有這樣才是真正守護一國兩制。<br />\n<br />\n香港人<br />\n2019.7.1"},{"pid":"bc7bca5252e12c0edfb8813d1c7a3824d385f2b9","tid":1273864,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:05:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd27ceb1f7f17abb964eadfbc33dde3df8ddfcf9","tid":1273864,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:05:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b518f4ba715e3641dfcc840554caaf623492a577","tid":1273864,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:08:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e899d006e23e1a5d9635de7179c2b3c2958cfab","tid":1273864,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:11:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff7371966ada1db5298ce24a4b7703c125b26e7f","tid":1273864,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:11:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5d2e1d5bf7f57f55cba11086914d25e54c8a9b92","tid":1273864,"uid":202803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:11:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa0ca2efa3455d801ae7ccbb7a60195cb5f30389","tid":1273864,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:11:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"382f2f650e489a1199ee2695722d9204881c3ba4","tid":1273864,"uid":90883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:11:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33272bfc74403819f8241531adacd553758ac134","tid":1273864,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec7422cf604deea3b9ebd454883eb55b5f07f4e","tid":1273864,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:11:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"38d1bd88eba797391a59db758c6b146fa5dcb5ee","tid":1273864,"uid":158499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f0c35b01f40613a61f92e11a1724bb0fec89a72","tid":1273864,"uid":192935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:12:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2472d3201e1b19429effc6d89759351f6e0096f3","tid":1273864,"uid":267395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:12:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"991207c1dc3268bde505e336464bc7b0df7c68aa","tid":1273864,"uid":72354,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:13:21.000Z","msg":"ID 26萬幾新會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪分散焦點<br />\n依家主要訴求係撤回惡法<br />\n講咁耐政府都唔理你<br />\n你轉移視線雙普選姐係由頭黎過<br />\n最後就乜都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec837c7fc0897579014b4f8381a74d4e2